HB NO. 2
1 Section 2. The election for which provision is made in this Act shall be held in
2 compliance with and subject to the applicable provisions of the Louisiana Election Code.
3 Section 3. Section 2 of Act No. 218 of the 2025 Regular Session of the Legislature
4 is hereby amended and reenacted to read as follows:
5 Section 2. Be it further resolved that this proposed amendment shall be
6 submitted to the electors of the state of Louisiana at a statewide election to be held
7 on April 18, 2026, if House Bill No. 625 of the 2025 Regular Session of the
8 Legislature of Louisiana becomes effective. If House Bill No. 625 of the 2025
9 Regular Session of the Legislature of Louisiana does not become effective, this
10 proposed amendment shall be submitted to the electors of the state of Louisiana at
11 a statewide election to be held on November 3, 2026. May 16, 2026.
12 Section 4. Section 2 of Act No. 219 of the 2025 Regular Session of the Legislature
13 is hereby amended and reenacted to read as follows:
14 Section 2. Be it further resolved that this proposed amendment shall be
15 submitted to the electors of the state of Louisiana at the statewide election to be held
16 on April 18, 2026. May 16, 2026.
17 Section 5. Section 3 of Act No. 221 of the 2025 Regular Session of the Legislature
18 is hereby amended and reenacted to read as follows:
19 Section 3. Be it further resolved that this proposed amendment shall be
20 submitted to the electors of the state of Louisiana at the statewide election to be held
21 on April 18, 2026. May 16, 2026.
22 Section 6. Section 8 of Act No. 222 of the 2025 Regular Session of the Legislature
23 is hereby amended and reenacted to read as follows:
24 Section 8. Be it further resolved that this proposed amendment shall be
25 submitted to the electors of the state of Louisiana at the statewide election to be held
26 on April 18, 2026. May 16, 2026.
27 Section 7. Section 2 of Act No. 223 of the 2025 Regular Session of the Legislature
28 is hereby amended and reenacted to read as follows:
